@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ==============================================
### 【1】GET 请求：查询用户（Read）
### ==============================================
### GET 获取所有用户列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/userList
Accept: application/json

### GET 根据用户ID查询单个用户 - 存在的情况
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/1
Accept: application/json

### GET 根据用户ID查询单个用户 - 不存在的情况（返回404）
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/99999
Accept: application/json

### ==============================================
### 【2】POST 请求：创建用户（Create）
### ==============================================
### POST 新增用户 - 成功
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "type": "student"
}

### POST 新增用户 - 用户名已存在（返回409）
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "duplicate@example.com",
  "type": "student"
}

### POST 新增用户 - 缺少用户名（返回400）
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "no-username@example.com",
  "type": "student"
}

### POST 新增用户 - 缺少密码（返回400）
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nopassword",
  "email": "no-password@example.com",
  "type": "student"
}

### ==============================================
### 【3】PUT 请求：更新用户信息（Update）
### ==============================================
### PUT 更新用户信息 - 成功
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "new_password_123",
  "email": "admin_updated@example.com",
  "type": "teacher"
}

### PUT 更新不存在的用户（返回404）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/99999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nonexistent",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "nonexistent@example.com",
  "type": "student"
}

### ==============================================
### 【4】DELETE 请求：删除用户（Delete）
### ==============================================
### DELETE 删除用户 - 成功
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user/2
Accept: application/json

### DELETE 删除不存在的用户（返回404）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user/99999
Accept: application/json

